description: "Designed to aid navigation around the western Java Sea, this map features bathymetry (sea depth), current and tide data, and is marked with shoals, reefs and other hazards. Written notes add details at specific locations (e.g. ‘heavy tide rips’)."
title: "Western   part   of   the   Java   Sea   :   from   Lucipara   I.   to   Sunda   Strait   and   Batavia,   corrected   to   1861"
